title: update to definition of guidance
body:
Clarifying the definition of guidance to make it clear that it is a set of input instructions to processes, tasks, etc.

This change is based on the following mailing list discussion.

https://www.ietf.org/mail-archive/web/sacm/current/msg04085.html
